      "term": "bemusements",
      "kind": "word",
      "cefrLevel": "C2",
      "senses": [
        {
          "pos": "noun",
          "definition": "plural of bemusement; states of being puzzled or confused and amused at the same time",
          "examples": [
            "Her bemusements grew as the lecture wandered into abstruse theory.",
            "The bemusements of the audience were evident as the comedian's joke landed oddly."
